MM7DTest - Tester program for MM7D air quality measuring device
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

1. About software
-----------------
  It is a tester program for MM7D device. You can retrieve information
  about software and measured data from device and set limit values to
  normal operating via HTTP and Modbus protocol.

Requirements:

  Hardware: PC, XT, AT or newer computer,
            8086 or newer processor,
            NIC.
  Software: FreeDOS,
            installed packet driver for NIC.

2. How to get installer package for my OS?
------------------------------------------
a. Visit homepage (see later) to download installer packages:

  DOS:      MM7DTT01.ZIP

b. Download from Github

  > git clone https://github.com/pozsarzs/mm7dtest.git

3. How to set the program?
-------------------------
  - If mTCP is not installed on your computer, edit MTCP.CFG file and
    set MTCPCFG environmental variable to this file. For example:
    > set mtcpcfg=c:\mm7dtest\mtcp.cfg

